    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scoping for a Class II device. CFD-predicted NIH values agree with FDA pump experimental data within 11.4% across all operating points, and the relative hemolysis index RH < 1 at the worst-case condition. The credibility evidence package is accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
